title: ../NEW 2024
presenter: Matt Wicks, Bryden Oliver & many others
eventShortDescription:
../NEW 2024 will be an in-person event, held 15th and 16th of May 2024 at Newcastle City Hall. It's a 2-day event comprised of talks and networking among the most innovative minds in the Sydney-Newcastle region.

SSW'ers presenting:
  • Matt Wicks
  • Bryden Oliver
  • and many more speakers!
Meet us there! 🙂

Note: SSW does not host this event.
